 experimental tests carried\nout at SwissFEL at the nominal beam charge of 200 pC confirmed the resilience\nto the heat-loading of the nano-fabricated WS. In this work, details on the\nnano-fabrication of free-standing WS as well as results of the electron-beam\ncharacterization are presented.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 20 Aug 2019 16:07:48 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 30 Jan 2020 12:37:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-04-22"}
