 to 0.20 mag in $E(B-V)$. A comparison with\nprevious reddening maps, based on the stellar components of the SMC, typically\nshows reasonable agreement. There is, however, significant variation amongst\nthe literature reddening maps as to the level of intrinsic reddening associated\nwith the bar. Thus, it is difficult to unambiguously state that instances of\nsignificant discrepancies are the result of appreciable levels of dust not\naccounted for in some literature reddening maps or whether they reflect issues\nwith our adopted methodology.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 20 Aug 2019 18:00:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-09-25"}
